description:
We had a wonderful night, parked in the parking lot, almost in front of the fireman. In case someone prefers, at the end of the street, there is the Motorhome club, a very nice structure and they charge 25 reais per person.

Tivemos uma noite maravilhosa, paramos no estacionamento, quase em frente o bombeiro. Caso alguém prefira, no final da rua, tem o clube do Motorhome, uma estrutura bem legal e cobram 25 reais por pessoa. 
@vanboratrilharomundo

Good rest area for the night, parked at the back and the noise in the camper was not noticeable. 

From Good Sam;
The State of Texas allows parking for up to 24 hours at any of their Rest Areas, Parking Areas or Roadside Picnic Areas, unless there are posted signs to the contrary.
